column10: Intersection at Columbia Pike and S Queen St. on multiple occasions drivers coming down the pike heading into DC run the light. We have had several near misses.
Aggressive driver passed me and my daughter (on bikes) on the right in the parking lane. Tailgated us and honked to threaten us before passing.
